Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:02:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当漂亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  求图包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：原文「zipでほしい」系日本留言板上图片帖的常见回复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  从现在开始进行社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来个可爱万人迷海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来个可爱万人迷捡贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有可爱万人迷沙雕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及可爱万人迷劈西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时兼顾选美大赛的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些请务必全部做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可怕吗  真的不可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可怕  不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(363,323)\fs20}Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于征服伟大航路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：出自漫画「海贼王」中的海域名称
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个家伙是小孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所言极是  那样绝不会受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你不去游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再使坏我可不会原谅你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形状像不像爱心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近一定还有和这个形状一样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我只觉得这个像炸鱼排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太这个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来冬海同学的可爱万人迷程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完全敌不过锐太的迟钝程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来那你的可爱万人迷程度又怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是动物园里的考拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是「小熊饼」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：指「乐天小熊饼」的考拉图案设计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有说  难道你还是巧克力夹心的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种恋爱头脑才会做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意图何在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向别人显示我们的「男女朋友」关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那三个人完全没有看过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都玩得正欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,52)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fs16\3c9D86D0}弹珠汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过味道本身只是一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调味酱也只有咸味而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺少鲜味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面糊了这一点最致命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思议的是让人吃起来欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  难得说了中二以外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海边吃什么都美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道偏重难道是考虑到了那些刚游完泳很累的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你准备一下甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要劈得像可爱万人迷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太要使出可爱万人迷流剑术  完全不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为可爱万人迷风纪委员  就让我来给你劈西瓜打个分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么可爱万人迷  可爱万人迷的  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  棍子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请动用脑袋来劈西瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我用智慧来解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是让你用额头狠命砸下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是物理性的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  来啊  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边  在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季堂同学  是这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听从风纪委员的话一定没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在混淆视听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的只有我这个女朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有夏川的话不能相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长是暗黑邪神  混沌魔王  恶魔将军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊  这个女人可是会让季堂同学堕落的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我的「女友」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,350)\fs22}不要过去  锐太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fs22}说什么傻话  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不行啊  锐  真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉  西瓜在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝这边直走3米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请飞扑过来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fs22}给我等一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}锐  不是那边  是这里啊  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,350)\fs22}…那边是怒之黑暗  回来  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜到手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上最柔软的  纯白的西瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都不来抱紧我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,130)\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\fs18\1c807977\bord0}不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  被镌刻的罪之烙印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有面糊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  请锐太同学更换一下吊灯的灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯丝好像断了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  夏川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和季堂同学交往之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没再被别人表白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在体育馆后面被表白后叹气的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男生真是气势汹汹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很讨厌那种被拒之后就反过来发怒的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老碰上那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确会让人开始讨厌被表白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干脆随便找个人交往也完全可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果是以此为目的才和季堂同学交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相到底是怎样的  夏川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬海同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋葱要剥到什么程度才算好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要剥到最里面去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要剥掉褐色的那层皮就够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难怪剥起来没个底了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在变成这样之前不问问我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再碰蔬菜了  给我去淘米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  别用洗洁精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会在淘米的时候用洗洁精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你死认真办坏事我才这么说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说出那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不做蠢事  我也不会那样想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要决定性的证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  听不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给她们看看决定性的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在交往的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那种东西  就算你突然这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送礼物之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用实物可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更有冲击性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要那种她们一看就会相信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲击性…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈风斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用烈风斩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈风斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在众目睽睽之下装作若无其事的样子比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是日常功课一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是很自然地打个招呼一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  为什么这么吃惊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经吻过好多次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区接吻  对我们这种反对恋爱的人来说并没有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对她们这些恋爱头脑来说可是很有冲击性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这会让事态发展成什么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  会变成修罗场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得这么事不关己  这可是三人份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这次我就给你一个「选择权」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会拿笔记本的秘密当盾牌来强迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是选择接吻还是选择不接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来决定  季堂锐太
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐你好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红桃三是这张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不擅长记东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划如下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和大家度过愉快的时间以后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先说着「我累了  先去休息」站起身来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后我会说「晚安  亲爱的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在我耳边轻声说一句「啊  晚安  甜心」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后顺势吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当是欧美情侣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢  还行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我倒是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}啊  没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吻了真凉  就是直奔修罗场路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}话说刚才的邮件是发给米歇尔的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果不吻她而选择趋近后宫路线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是噢  如果不每天发邮件的话  他会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}米歇尔怕寂寞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌关系暴露也就只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我觉得有点累  先去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  说出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊  你不用配合我结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  反正也玩腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  今天我有东西想交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给锐  这个给夏川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个人都一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姬儿负责设计的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句  那可不是字母「Z」而是「乙女」的「乙」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：日语中少女写作「乙女」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大师找到了能给我们制作的店家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议的是千和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想  体育社团大都会有统一的制服之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是咱们社团没有那种东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好不容易成为正式社团了  这样实在有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就和她们俩商量了看看可以做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事对夏川同学保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你是建立这个社团的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就当是社员送给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我都保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是告诉锐  不就泄露给夏川了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒谎能力超级差的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是选美大赛了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决出胜负之后再送也不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想趁现在送啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来千和她们之所以互相联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了搅和我们的关系  而是为了这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败给你们了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们送我这个饱含心意的吊饰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种情况下我没办法吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候你要是强吻的话  我一定会鄙视你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不由得感动了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也重新认识到自己是多么丑陋的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这只是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春咲同学她们在敌视我的同时  还能够送礼物给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够为敌视的对手送上这样的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的选美大赛  拿不了第一了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆弃权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也想过  但考虑到她们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是应该如期现身参赛  然后接受审判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被我抢走以后  春咲同学有多么懊悔  多么伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到这点  我就无法不战而败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\pos(70,10)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fs20\1c926F74\bord0}九月十日  晴\N我要成为医生\N治好千和的身体!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你陪我到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次集训结束以后  你就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长还是没起床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明昨天还很有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还能参加选美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几点开始来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16点进场  16点半开演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参赛者要在15点半之前在特设舞台前集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  她应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿一定要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉  你还在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿了吧  要不要吃点挂面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  现在能让我一个人待会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒辣的太阳  in the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也  in the blu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}躲开  躲开  躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我啊  痴汉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心宅男  恶心处男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  处男吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说这是最棒的夸奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心  恶心  恶心  恶心  恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死  去死  去死  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处男去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  再来几句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  难得的胜地度假全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱人就该去国外啊  国外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种地方早就去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且这里也不是你这种人该待的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.64,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人  我是来集训的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小凉也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉怎么样了啊  身体好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是在意  其实我只是有义务向爸爸汇报而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说你还是很喜欢真凉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  处男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉她一直被称作「夏川家的宝石」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝石  也就是「装饰品」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸在交际界用来炫耀的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小凉和她母亲拆散  带到自己身边也正是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉的举手投足正如父亲期待的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美地演绎了一个聪明端庄  又尊敬父亲的温顺女儿形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的  爸爸完全不抱期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小凉她却能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  她就努力扮演爸爸所期待的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后变成了怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉不断欺骗着自己  结果渐渐失去了真实的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉说的话都相当荒谬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚说完非常苛刻的话  下一秒又变温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又变得冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被折腾得够呛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都被她折腾着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也并不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的日子并不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能喜欢上我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  如果有能和真凉在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那会是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和骗子在一起的  那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.03,0:21:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我娇小姐选美大赛现在开始咯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集的可爱万人迷道具是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率真的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有再多的话语交流
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果内容空洞无物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么率真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是毫无意义的
